Ask HN: Toys or materials to teach 3 year olds “programming”?
text: Hi, I'm looking for some fun materials that would help my boys to develop interest in basic concepts of programming like procedures, types or loops. I know some of you will probably tell me it's too early and that at this age it's all about building relations and whatnot, but they already seem to be way smarter than I expected them to be so why not point them in a new direction? Anyway, any ideas are appreciated :)

Show HN: Codeium – a free, ultrafast AI codegen extension
text:
I'm Varun, CEO of Exafunction, and we just released Codeium to open up access of generative AI to all developers for free. In the spirit of Show HN, we created a playground version for anyone to try this tech in the browser (click Try in Browser)!

We have built scalable, low-latency ML infra for many top AI companies in the past, and we are excited to leverage that tech into a product that we, as developers, would love. We hope that you do too, and we would appreciate any feedback that this community has for us!
